title: Tor, Gpass, Freenet and Freegate
description:
This is a collection of installers and executables for internet censorship circumvention.  

These are a pain to download in China (unless you've already got a circumvention tool), but torrents are easy.  So why not make a torrent with this stuff?

I don't know if all of these work in China, I can only verify Gpass and Freegate.  YMMV elsewhere.  Regardless, one of these is likely to work wherever you are.
